Package: rvt
Title: Relief Visualization Toolbox for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Nick", "Gauthier", , "ngauthier@ufl.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6605-3470")),
    person("Anthropic", "Claude", role = "aut",
           comment = "R port of rvt-py algorithms")
  )
Description: Pure R implementation of the Relief Visualization Toolbox (RVT)
    algorithms for terrain visualization from LiDAR data. Computes hillshade,
    slope, sky-view factor, positive openness, simple local relief model, and
    the Visualization for Archaeological Topography (VAT) composite blend.
    Faithful port of rvt-py (Kokalj et al.) with no Python dependency.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/flmnh-ai/rvt
BugReports: https://github.com/flmnh-ai/rvt/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.4.0)
Suggests:
    terra,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
